## Second tree ((Sp1_03:0.3,Sp1_04:0.2):0.3,(Sp2_02:0.8,Sp3_03:0.4):0.4));
## Expected topology should be: ((Sp1:1,Sp1:1):1,(Sp2:1,Sp3:1):1)

